# Plot MDS

  x = "Dim.1", y = "Dim.2",
  size = 1, repel = TRUE
) +
  ggrepel::geom_text_repel(

  )


df <- read.csv("stage4_bogota3_edge.csv")
df
# K-means clustering
clust <- kmeans(mds, 3)$cluster %>%
  as.factor()
mds <- mds %>%
  mutate(groups = clust)
# Plot and color by groups
ggscatter(mds, x = "Dim.1", y = "Dim.2", 
          label = rownames(df),
          color = "groups",
          palette = "jco",
          title = "Stage 4 Full Transparency", 
          size = 1, 
          ellipse = TRUE,
          ellipse.type = "convex",
          repel = TRUE)
